Class ClientRouterManagement

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    public class ClientRouterManagement
extends AConnectionManager
implements java.lang.Runnable

    The class of ClientRouterManagement is used to abstractly define the type of the instances.

    These instances are responsible for managing connection with router from client.

    Written for project "Connections2".
